                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-8-victim116 t18151025-8-viclabel41"></join>. I let lodgings in that house; I let a room to the prisoner, on the night of the 7th of October. The things stolen were let to him. In the morning, the sheets and the pillow case were missing. Just after the prisoner was gone, my servant brought him back; and I saw the sheets taken from his person; one was folded down his back, and the other down his stomach.</p>
               <p>(Property produced, and sworn to)</p>
